sem1 <- sem(
  "Allow =~ imsmetn1 + imdfetn1 + impcntr1;
  Symbolic =~ imueclt + imwbcnt + imbgeco;
  Universalism =~ ipeqopt.rec + ipudrst.rec;
  Conformity =~ ipfrule.rec + ipmodst.rec + ipbhprp.rec + imptrad.rec;
  Soctrust =~ pplhlp + ppltrst + pplfair;
  
  # regression
  Allow  ~ Universalism + Conformity;
  Symbolic ~ Universalism + Conformity;
  Soctrust ~ Universalism + Conformity;
  
  # control variables
  Allow + Symbolic + Soctrust ~ agea + gndr + income + eisced ;
           
  ",
  data[data$cntry == "RU",],
  estimator = "ml",
  missing = "listwise"
)
